{"tid":1578923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首\"肥媽有話兒\"真係好過果首\"喪曲回歸於香港\"太多喇","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T01:55:19.000Z","uid":241151,"like":9,"dislike":183,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa77c800b0e1807fe753a286e11249e0391ec3c","tid":1578923,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nHzXk5bPmrQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnHzXk5bPmrQ&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=dbf477cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nHzXk5bPmrQ</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;肥媽有話兒&quot;刺激到群眾情緒，又夠洗腦，又好玩，又開心<br />\n<br />\n&quot;榮光歸於香港&quot;成隻喪曲咁，歌又唔係好聽過人，又難記，又唔pop，又振奮唔到士氣，內容意思仲衰過海濶天空，剩係一尾賣慘，簡直就係同成日靠賣慘既泛民和理非左膠夾到癲，之前有成個禮拜個抗爭死氣沉沉，忽然膠化晒變和理非，抗爭者開始灰心，係得果班和理非一味自己話贏緊(我諗佢地既真正意思係想講和理非贏咗勇武，維穩成功！)，差d搞死咗個抗爭，作呢首歌既人同埋之前狂推呢首歌既傳媒同網媒個好明顯其心不正，用心不良！"},{"pid":"2862d66e0b34d5044f73d2f715ccdff6f647628c","tid":1578923,"uid":62025,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"三毛blocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c02c64fd0aab2060d8085eba6a1129d97a7021e","tid":1578923,"uid":253016,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"你老母就喪曲"},{"pid":"62c8b7a3bc8bf48a87fcdb78293219f2d0ec30de","tid":1578923,"uid":4006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"Blocked 上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f867d35a31d321727d874be49a89505bfbd919d","tid":1578923,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">善用不推文回覆</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0938a9ad77e83642af43e458d6e66779000fd19d","tid":1578923,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"<span s